    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is offset by the direct 1:1 correspondence between the validation scenario and the COU, the multi-laboratory test program, and the conservative acceptance thresholds applied. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium model risk level decision. Package accepted with notation of the test conditions limitation.",
